messages.messageBody:
> From: Samantha Stopple <sammimag@...>
> We live in Monroe, WA. Maybe we will see yah next time
> you go to the tracking club. You can't miss us we are
> the family with two young kids 5yrs and 2yrs.

Small world - my hubby and I were married in Monroe, WA. In the big old
brick Methodist church on the street coming into town from Duvall (can't
remember the highway number). We went to church there for years, but lived
in Duvall. Also used to fly in and out of the little airport there from time
to time, it's a hairy approach coming in right over the fairgrounds. Great
town!

Blue Skies!
-Robin-
Mom to Mackenzie (8/28/96) who is playing his Christmas guitar
and Asa (10/5/99) who is playing the harmonica to accompany her brother
